  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿！你好，近期如何？我这儿有个小任务，你感兴趣吗？希望如此，哈哈哈...基本上我的团队需要一些新的背包。有时候在搜刮完之后，他们经常会因为陷入苦战而不得不丢掉背包以增加生还的可能性。\n\n同时对我而言也是更需要人力而不是一些战利品。但这让我们的好背包很快就用完了，所以我希望你能带一些中型背包给我们。\n\n我不在乎你从哪里弄到它们，但如果你选择从别人那里拿，我建议你干掉一些当地居民和Raider们，看看他们的装备如何，可能有我们需要的背包。最后再次祝你一路顺风！",
    "en": "Hello. I have a small job for you again, you interested? I hope so haha, basically my group needs a few new backpacks. Sometimes after looting up they get into fights and need to throw the bag away to increase their survival chance.\n\nI need manpower more than some loot. That makes us run out of good backpacks really quickly, so I want you to bring us a few medium-sized backpacks.\n\nI don't care where you get them from, but if you choose to take them from someone else, I recommend that you drop some scav raiders and check their gear, they might have some of those we want. Good luck again!"
  },
